Package: lapisR
Title: Retrieving data from LAPIS
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Chaoran", "Chen")
    person("Mara", "Neacsu")
Description: lapisR provides functions for retrieving data from various LAPIS endpoints. These include functions requesting database statistics, sets of sequences and their metadata, sets of mutations or insertions, and sequence alignments.
URL: https://github.com/GenSpectrum/lapisR/
BugReports: https://github.com/GenSpectrum/lapisR/issues
